pig dog
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:one of several breeds of dog used for hunting wild pigs.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: specifically may be a bailer, finder, or holder
